org.eclipse.viatra.dse.objectives.impl

Class WeightedQueriesSoftObjective

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.viatra.dse.objectives.impl.BaseObjective
      • org.eclipse.viatra.dse.objectives.impl.WeightedQueriesSoftObjective
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IObjective
    Deprecated. 
    Use ConstraintsObjective instead.

    @Deprecated
public class WeightedQueriesSoftObjective
extends BaseObjective
    This soft objective collects a list of VIATRA queries and weights. Then the fitness value of a solution is calculated in the following way:

    fitness = sum( pattern[i].countMatches() * weight[i] )

    See Also:
